### Steps to Reproduce:

1. Create a `.scss` file
2. Paste the following code:
```
$default-margin: 20px;

.mar{
	/* Margin classes */
	&-t{
		margin-top: $default-margin;

		&-0{
			margin-top: 0;
		}
	}
}
```
3. View -> Problems


### Additional Notes: 
All the extensions were disabled.


